OL,3,CFormer Conservative MP Danny Kruger
OL,4,Cdefects to Reform UK
OL,6,FThe MP for East Wiltshire, Danny
OL,7,FKruger, has defected from the
OL,8,FConservative Party to Reform UK,
OL,9,Fsaying he hopes the next prime
OL,10,Fminister will be Nigel Farage.
OL,12,FIn a speech on Monday morning, Mr
OL,13,FKruger said his former party "is over"
OL,14,Fand is no longer "the principal
OL,15,Fopposition to the left".
OL,17,F"But I am not despondent because
OL,18,Fconservatism is not over," Mr Kruger
OL,19,Fsaid at a press conference in London.
