OL,3,CFormer Conservative MP Danny Kruger
OL,4,Cdefects to Reform UK
OL,6,F"It's never been needed more. And
OL,7,Factually, it's never been more
OL,8,Fvibrant. Because the failure of the
OL,9,FConservative Party has created space
OL,10,Ffor an alternative. The flame is
OL,11,Fpassing from one torch to another."
OL,13,FThe MP, who has represented East
OL,14,FWiltshire, previously Devizes, since
OL,15,F2019, said his role will be preparing
OL,16,FFarage's Party for government.
