OL,3,CFormer Conservative MP Danny Kruger
OL,4,Cdefects to Reform UK
OL,6,FKemi Badenoch, the Conservative Party
OL,7,Fleader, recently gave him a role in
OL,8,Fher shadow cabinet as a minister for
OL,9,Fwork and pensions, and he led the
OL,10,Fparliamentary campaign against the
OL,11,Flegalisation of assisted dying.
OL,13,FOn the defection, Mr Kruger insisted:
OL,14,F"I'm not jumping to save my skin."
OL,15,FThis is "a very significant personal
OL,16,Frisk", he added.
OL,18,FAt the 2024 general election, Mr
OL,19,FKruger was re-elected as a
OL,20,FConservative MP with a majority of
OL,21,F4,716.
